Now we can do things like group the data by turn, and get a new dataframe summarized by turn.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
transcription |> 
  mutate(
    turn = consecutive_id(speaker)
  ) |> 
  summarise(
    .by = c(turn, speaker),
    start = min(start),
    end = max(end),
    transcript = str_c(transcript, collapse = " "),
  )
```
